type: web_research
title: Claude Code Chat UI / MCP Web Interface / Non-developer Access - Comprehensive Research 2026
key_insights[12]: "Anthropic officially launched claude.ai/code - a web-based Claude Code with GitHub integration, parallel sessions, teleport to CLI, and iOS mobile support",Claude Code now has official Slack integration (research preview) - @mention triggers Code sessions,Claude Code SDK provides headless mode (-p flag) and Python/TypeScript SDKs for programmatic access,MCP Apps (Jan 2026) extends MCP to render interactive UI widgets in chat windows - cross-platform with ChatGPT/VS Code/Goose,LINE Bot MCP Server (github.com/line/line-bot-mcp-server) enables Claude-to-LINE Official Account messaging,"Open-source web UIs: sugyan/claude-code-webui (675 stars), siteboon/claudecodeui (CloudCLI), andrepimenta/claude-code-chat (VS Code)","LibreChat, LobeChat, Open WebUI, AnythingLLM, 5ire all support MCP integration with chat UIs","Chat-MCP Bridge provides decoupled architecture: React frontend + Event Hub API + MCP Server via SSE",Claude Code hit $1B revenue in 6 months; Rakuten reduced dev timelines 79% using it,Pro/Max plans include both claude.ai and Claude Code under one subscription,Claude Chic (uvx claudechic) provides improved terminal skin for Claude Code,"MCP Apps launch partners: Amplitude, Asana, Box, Canva, Clay, Figma, Hex, monday.com, Slack"
findings[10]: "claude.ai/code is the official web UI - runs in Anthropic cloud containers, creates PRs, supports parallel sessions","Claude Code SDK headless mode: claude -p 'prompt' for non-interactive execution in CI/CD","Python SDK: query() async function, ClaudeSDKClient with custom tools/hooks as Python functions","MCP Apps use iframe sandboxing, pre-declared templates, JSON-RPC communication for security","LibreChat supports stdio/streamable HTTP-SSE transport, multi-user isolation, YAML config for MCP",Open WebUI uses Pipeline initiative for extending tools - no native MCP but extensible,"LINE Bot MCP Server: push text/flex messages via LINE Messaging API, works with Claude Desktop/Cline","CloudCLI (Claude Code UI): React/Vite frontend + Express/WebSocket backend + Claude CLI integration","claude-code-webui: Hono backend + React frontend, supports Deno and Node.js, SSE streaming","MCP tool search (Jan 2026): lazy loading improved Opus 4.5 accuracy from 79.5% to 88.1%"
recommendations[7]: "For non-developer chat access: Use claude.ai/code (official) or CloudCLI for remote mobile/web access","For Slack integration: Use official Claude Code in Slack (research preview) or mpociot/claude-code-slack-bot","For LINE integration: Use line/line-bot-mcp-server with Claude Desktop or custom MCP client","For self-hosted chat UI with MCP: LibreChat is the most enterprise-ready option","For programmatic access: Use Claude Code SDK (Python/TypeScript) with headless mode","For custom chat UI: Build on Chat-MCP Bridge pattern (React + Event Hub + MCP Server)","For mobile access: CloudCLI + Cloudflare Tunnel or official claude.ai/code on iOS"
